<div class="d-panels font-secondary-light">
<div id="aip_a" class="d-panel p" style="display: none">
<div class="p" id="aff1">
<sup>1</sup>Shiley Eye Center, University of California-San Diego, La Jolla, California, United States
</div>
<div id="aff2">
<sup>2</sup>Ophthalmic Genetics and Visual Function Branch, National Eye Institute, National Institutes of Health, Bethesda, Maryland, United States
